# /etc/fw_env.config - intentionally empty for am3-bb-s19jpro.
#
# Provenance: derived from board/beaglebone/am3-bb/rootfs-overlay/etc/fw_env.config.
# Wave reference: AGENT B3 wave W10.x (2026-05-09).
#
# AGENT B3 cross-checked PORTING_PLAN.md section 4: the reconstructed
# AM335x BB U-Boot uses CONFIG_ENV_IS_NOWHERE -- there is no persistent
# fw_env partition, no validated NAND offset, and no /dev/nand_env-style
# environment device. Until live evidence pins an exact MTD offset (per
# ), no fw_env.config
# entry is safe.
#
# Keep this file present with comments only so accidental fw_printenv /
# fw_setenv calls fail closed instead of writing the wrong device.
